    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;A standard set of information fields is defined as the first version of an Electronic Commerce Modeling Language (ECML) so that this task can be more easily automated, for example by wallet software that could fill in fields.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
